Use the standard library
This is how to sum_to_n of n:
   Remember that total is 0
   Remember that i is 1
   Do this n times:
      Remember that total is sum of total and i
      Increase i
   End do
   The answer is total
Now you know
>>> sum_to_n of 30 
465
>>> sum_to_n of 100 
5050
>>> sum_to_n of 5 
15
>>> sum_to_n of 10 
55
>>> sum_to_n of 1 
1
>>> sum_to_n of 1 
1
>>> sum_to_n of 6 
21
>>> sum_to_n of 11 
66
>>> sum_to_n of 30 
465
>>> sum_to_n of 100 
5050
